# ─── AI Assistant Configuration ──────────────────────────────────────────────
#
# Most settings can be configured via the web admin panel at /d/admin
# after running: node scripts/install.mjs && npm start
#
# This file only needs DASHBOARD_PORT for first boot.
# All other values can be entered via the setup wizard at /setup.
#
# If you prefer to configure via this file instead of the web UI,
# fill in the values below and they will take precedence over the admin panel.

# ─── Dashboard ───────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# Port for the web dashboard (default: 3456)
DASHBOARD_PORT=3456

# Public URL for dashboard links and Google OAuth callback (use your VPS IP).
# Required for Google OAuth to work — Vercel posts tokens to this URL.
DASHBOARD_URL=http://YOUR_IP:3456

# ─── Telegram ────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# Get this from @BotFather on Telegram (/newbot)
# Can also be configured via /setup wizard.
TELEGRAM_BOT_TOKEN=

# Your Telegram numeric user ID (from @userinfobot).
# The bot will silently ignore messages from anyone else.
ALLOWED_TELEGRAM_USER_ID=

# ─── Model ────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# Claude CLI model alias or full model name.
# Aliases:  opus | sonnet | haiku
# No API key needed — uses your Claude Max subscription via the claude CLI.
CLAUDE_MODEL=opus

# ─── Timezone ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# IANA timezone (default: UTC). Set via admin panel or here.
# TIMEZONE=America/New_York

# ─── Google (Gmail + Drive + Calendar) ────────────────────────────────────────
# Pre-configured OAuth 2.0 credentials. Client just clicks "Connect to Google".
GOOGLE_CLIENT_ID=YOUR_GOOGLE_CLIENT_ID
GOOGLE_CLIENT_SECRET=YOUR_GOOGLE_CLIENT_SECRET

# ─── Google OAuth Handler (Vercel) ──────────────────────────────────────────
# Central HTTPS OAuth handler deployed on Vercel (free tier).
# Handles the Google OAuth callback with automatic HTTPS — no Caddy/DuckDNS needed.
#
# Deploy once:
#   cd vercel-oauth && npx vercel --prod
#   Set env vars in Vercel: GOOGLE_CLIENT_ID, GOOGLE_CLIENT_SECRET, STATE_SECRET
#   Register the redirect URI in Google Console: https://YOUR_APP.vercel.app/api/oauth
#
# Then set this to your Vercel function URL:
OAUTH_HANDLER_URL=https://YOUR_APP.vercel.app/api/oauth

# ─── Todoist ──────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# Personal API token from todoist.com → Settings → Integrations → Developer
# TODOIST_API_TOKEN=

# ─── Freedcamp ────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# API credentials from Freedcamp settings
# FREEDCAMP_API_KEY=
# FREEDCAMP_API_SECRET=

# ─── Evernote ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# Developer token for Evernote API (optional)
# EVERNOTE_TOKEN=
# EVERNOTE_SANDBOX=false

# ─── Google Drive ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# Folder name in Google Drive for uploaded documents (default: AI Assistant)
# DRIVE_FOLDER=AI Assistant

# ─── Scheduler ───────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# Automatic morning briefing time (HH:MM in local timezone)
# Sends Freedcamp tasks, Todoist, calendar, goals, and unread emails.
# SCHEDULE_MORNING=08:30

# Automatic weekly summary (DAY:HH:MM — e.g. FRI:16:00)
# Sends week-in-review with accomplishments, stalled items, and next-week focus.
# SCHEDULE_WEEKLY=FRI:16:00

# ─── Limits ───────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# Max conversation turns kept in memory per chat session
MAX_HISTORY_TURNS=20
